snippet.title: Let's Play Bullet Audyssey: Dance to the bullets!
snippet.description:
https://patreon.com/TheZeldaZone A masterfully well designed rhythm/bullet hell shooter combo.
Play it here: http://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/584352

You may recall Beat Chaser 2 (http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=38cflIxbeI4) a similar game; this one actually came out a couple years earlier!  💬 https://zelda.zone/discord

Comment a timestamp if I missed something!
